{"tid":2101681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唉......返工比人針對好唔開心","createTime":"2020-07-10T03:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T03:46:03.000Z","uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47a8301bae37bd7d374d078f4bed113656497d0e","tid":2101681,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:34:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">我返左份政府工，agent介紹既，都返左五個月啦，主要係做BO既，平日同公司同事既關係幾好，因為我工作經常關連兩個team，所以經常要行黎行去，我果team既上司份人好軟，隔離team既上司就好強勢，最近成日比隔離team既上司針對，未有先向我上司報告情況就直接走向經理到投訴我成日做錯野，三日唔埋兩日又投訴一輪，投訴親都係小事，例如打錯字/開錯檔，都是可以自己內部解決，但我上司每次都是經鄰team投訴完後經理走去了解先後知後覺，但又未真正了解清楚就先認錯，沒有要保護下屬的態度，搞到鄰team上司不斷投訴我搞到小事化大，有時人人都有責任負時就把我推出去當炮灰，要我負全責，還要扣我錢，但我上班是要搵錢，不是要扣錢。而且還要寫report解釋又要開會，所以我做得很不開心。</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e79032f361ba52522b93c213943012772f851ddc","tid":2101681,"uid":63822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">日日話手足係condom<br />\n要接管晒手足的女人</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#56875 - 人善被人J</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (5)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fyDErT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fyDErT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxtKzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxtKzT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxnxcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxnxcT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxifnT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxifnT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxidMT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxidMT</a><span st